msgstr "自己資本利益率（ROE）"

#: templates/stock/explanation.html:46
msgid ""
"A quantification of how much profit a company has made with the money "
"invested by its shareholders."
msgstr ""
"株主が出資したお金を元手に、企業がどれだけの利益を上げたのかを数値化したも"
"の。"

#: templates/stock/explanation.html:47
msgid ""
"In other words, it is a financial indicator that shows how efficiently the "
"company is earning money."
msgstr ""
"言い換えると、「企業がどれぐらい効率良くお金を稼いでいるか」を示す財務指標で"
"ある。"

